edu.pjatk.inn.coffeemaker.impl

Class Recipe

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.pjatk.inn.coffeemaker.impl.Recipe
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Recipe
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class representing a recipe for a coffee drink. Contains information about the name, price, and ingredients (coffee, milk, sugar, chocolate) of the recipe. Implements Serializable interface to allow for storage and retrieval of recipe objects.
    Author:
    Sarah and Mike
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
